comments: What Michael said!!!!  Song For My Father is to this moment one of the most beautiful works of music ever and the LP is a cover to cover classic

Like Duke Horace is a name synonymous with the piano Horace Ward Martin Tavares Silva is very rhythmic & soulful.Like the others.He plays a very hip and powerful stride style but what really makes him unique is his pen. Horace has written some of the hippest & most sophisticated, complicated & clever tunes ever written and cats just don't end tune like He does anymore. Peace
